<h2 id="common-shortcuts">Common shortcuts</h2>

<p>Some shortcuts are available for all the representations (diagram, table, treeâ€¦).</p>

<table width="100%" border="0">
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 20%;" />
<col style="width: 30%; text-align: center;" />
